title: 123: The Shark Tank Haul Episode
itunes:title: The Shark Tank Haul Episode
description: Lisa and the gang are taste testing cool Shark Tank products like Genius Coconut Smoothies, Ka-Pop! Puffs, a super-tasty date spread,and more! Plus, the gang tries out a very inventive spatula that can be used for virtually anything! And make sure you’re listening to every second so you can find out how to win Lisa’s Touch Screen Purse that’s featured in the episode! So grab your swimsuits, we’re diving head first into the Shark Tank, and when you're done drying off, head on over to the Foodcast page for all the products mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: We’re taking a deep dive and trying JAWSOME products featured on Shark Tank in this week’s episode of Chew the Right Thing!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
